data.description: A nice Single-Family home in wonderful Viewpoint North subdivision. Home highlights an open & spacious split floor-plan with 2 bedrooms plus an office, 2 bathrooms, front courtyard area, and a 2 car garage.  Functional kitchen has an abundant amount of oak cabinets with a dining area. Kitchen also opens to a spacious living room with a cozy fireplace. Nice master bedroom and has a 3/4 bathroom, shower, dual vanity and large walk-in closet.  Spacious covered back patio leads to backyard with a privacy block wall.
